        "title": "fix: hide Skill Workshop revision handoff from chat",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Add `skills.proposals.requestRevision` so Skill Workshop revision requests keep the visible user message separate from server-built agent instructions.\r\n- Route Skill Workshop revision sends through the new RPC from the UI, including queued-send metadata and composer persistence for reconnect/retry safety.\r\n- Validate that the proposal exists and is pending before starting the revision turn.\r\n- Keep proposal workspace ownership separate from the target chat agent/session.\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n<img width=\"1300\" height=\"417\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d8f3a741-8d5d-4e02-bddb-f398c942f1f2\" />\r\n\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n<img width=\"1304\" height=\"426\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e60c01b2-6fe2-49eb-9d0d-0a717e2442cc\" />\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n\r\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs packages/gateway-protocol/src/index.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods/skills.proposals.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat/composer-persistence.test.ts`\r\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.ui.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/test-ui-skill-workshop-revision-handoff.tsbuildinfo`\r\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.src.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/test-src-skill-workshop-revision-handoff.tsbuildinfo`\r\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.packages.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/test-packages-skill-workshop-revision-handoff.tsbuildinfo`\r\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs ...touched files...`\r\n- `git diff --check HEAD~3..HEAD`\r\n- Blacksmith Testbox through Crabbox: `corepack pnpm check:changed` on `tbx_01kt7wj9fr2zsrsbn1neh87cqn`\r\n",
